name: Juanita: A Family Mystery
overview: Journalist Juanita Nielsen's family pursue the truth about her infamous 1975 disappearance. Revelations about Juanita's almost certain murder and remarkable life go to who killed her, why and how justice was denied.

episodes.name: Episode 1
